# MisJuegos v2 harness

**Start every session:** read `AGENTS.md` at repo root.

## Locked decisions (do not change without Jorge)

- No anonymous login → use `participants`
- Private group RLS (authenticated members read shared data)
- `session_messages` + `board_game_scores` in Phase 5 migrations
- Fresh start — no v1 DB migration; Sheets/Drive = one-time import only
- Catalog (`game_catalog`) separate from sessions (`play_sessions`)

## Architecture

Views → Composables → Services → Supabase. Pinia for auth/UI only — not a DB cache.

## When finishing work

1. Run `pnpm test`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm build`
2. Suggest a **Conventional Commits** message to Jorge
3. Do **not** commit unless asked
4. Update phase status in `AGENTS.md` / `docs/ROADMAP.md` if a phase completed

## UX

- Spanish UI copy; brand colors in Tailwind (`dark`, `primary`, `secondary`, `tertiary`)
- **Preserve v1 animations** — see `docs/UI_ANIMATIONS.md` (Phase 3+)

